== Build the skeleton

1. Load the defconfig

    $ make skeleton_defconfig

2. Initialize the module repository

    $ make init

3. Build the module FW image

    $ make


== Build the skeleton with an alternative nuttx directory

1. Load the defconfig

    $ make skeleton_defconfig

2. Initialize the module repository

    $ NUTTX_ROOT=/path/to/nuttx make init

3. Build the module FW image

    $ NUTTX_ROOT=/path/to/nuttx make
